
### 8. **`setup.py`**

```python
from setuptools import setup, find_packages

setup(
    name="breach-research",
    version="1.0.0",
    description="Research tool for credential stuffing analysis",
    author="[Il Tuo Nome]",
    author_email="[tua.email@universita.it]",
    packages=find_packages(),
    install_requires=[
        "numpy>=1.24.0",
        "psutil>=5.9.0",
        "tqdm>=4.65.0",
        "pandas>=2.0.0",
        "matplotlib>=3.7.0",
        "click>=8.1.0",
    ],
    entry_points={
        "console_scripts": [
            "breach-research=main:cli",
        ],
    },
    python_requires=">=3.8",
)